      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(imessage): send group media via attachment command",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nRecreates #86720 after #86734 reverted it so the #83365 iMessage group media fix can go through a clean review cycle.\n\nFixes iMessage media-only sends to explicit chat targets by routing them through `imsg send-attachment --transport auto` instead of the generic RPC `send` payload with a file path.\n\n## Why\n\nWhile testing #83365 on Lobster, normal iMessage group image replies generated the PNG but did not deliver a media attachment. Direct `imsg send-rich --file` also failed on the same group with an IMCore attachment staging error, while `imsg send-attachment --transport auto` succeeded and produced a real attachment row.\n\nDM media sends by handle already worked, so this keeps handle/DM sends on the existing path and only changes explicit chat media-only sends (`chat_id` / `chat_guid`).\n\n## Changes\n\n- Add a CLI JSON helper for the iMessage send runtime.\n- For media-only explicit chat sends, resolve `chat_id` to a chat GUID when needed and call `send-attachment --transport auto`.\n- Preserve existing RPC send behavior for DM handle media sends and text/caption sends.\n- Add unit coverage for chat GUID, chat ID, and DM handle media behavior.\n\n## Prior work / credit\n\nThis intentionally recreates the previously merged #86720 after its procedural revert in #86734. Original fix and Lobster proof by @omarshahine.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nLobster Mac proof from #86720 / #83365:\n\n- Generated media-only iMessage group reply produced the PNG but did not land through the normal send path.\n- Direct `imsg send-rich --file` failed for the same group with an IMCore staging error.\n- `imsg send-attachment --transport auto` succeeded and produced a visible attachment row in the group chat.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `git diff --cached --check`\n- `pnpm format:check -- extensions/imessage/src/send.ts extensions/imessage/src/send.test.ts`\n- `pnpm test extensions/imessage/src/send.test.ts extensions/imessage/src/actions.runtime.test.ts`\n- `pnpm tsgo:extensions`\n\nFixes #83365\n",
